// card.xrs — a reusable UI component in its own file (spec 20 Cut 2). Imported
// by pass_import_component.xrs. `pub` is what makes it crossable. Not a fixture
// itself; the harness skips non-pass_/fail_ files.
pub ui component Badge(label: String, color: String) {
    view {
        box {
            text label
            style "padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 4px; color: white;"
        }
    }
}
